title: Выживалити. Миссия Альфа
overview: 14 Russian reality stars in the fight for 10 million rubles. They were sure that they were going to another reality show, but ended up in a survival game. 24/7 they will undergo the toughest physical tests and cunning psychological traps in the history of Russian television. They will be tempted by money and power. What will they do for 10 million rubles and will they remain human?
